          BAJA SUR SURPLUS PAINT EXPORT BUSINESS PLAN (OC TO BAJA)
================================================================================

[1. BUSINESS CONCEPT & HIGHLIGHTS]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Strategy: Source premium "Mistint/Mis-tint" paint buckets from Orange County 
  (OC), California at liquidation prices. Export legally to remote towns in 
  Baja California / Baja California Sur (Bahía de los Ángeles, Guerrero Negro).
* Value Proposition: Remote Baja towns face high freight costs and low supply 
  for high-quality American paint. Sells fast at a massive premium.
* Target Sale Price in Baja: $3,400 MXN (~$195 USD) per 5-gallon bucket.

